                </p>
                <input type="password" id="secretVerificationInput" class="secret-input" placeholder="• • • • • • • • • •" maxlength="32" autocomplete="off" onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')verifySecretAndLogin();">
                <p style="font-size:10px;color:var(--gray-400);margin-top:6px;">ይህ ቁልፍ ለአድሚኑ ብቻ የሚታወቅ ነው</p>
